    <h2 id="howOften">How often should I water?</h2>
    <br>
    <p>Needed watering frequency changes by plant, season, development stage, etc. The best way to keep track of these needs is through research and planning, using our watering scheduler, and to monitor your plant for signs of dehydration. Keep in mind that a lot of plants need to have their soil fully dry between waterings. Too much water, a poorly draining environment, or consistently wet conditions around the roots can cause root rot. </p>
